Package: futurehelper
Title: Convenient Setup of Future Plans
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Bradley", "Buchsbaum", email = "brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com",
                   role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a simple interface for initializing 'future' parallel
    evaluation plans without needing to remember the various plan constructors
    and tweaking syntax. Supports multicore, multisession, and callr backends
    with sensible defaults for memory limits and worker counts.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports:
    future,
    parallelly
Suggests:
    future.callr,
    future.mirai
